# 🤖 AI Knowledge Base Assistant

An AI-powered Knowledge Base Assistant built with **n8n**, **Google Gemini**, and **Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)**.

This project automatically collects Question & Answer submissions through a form, enriches them using AI-generated tags, stores them in a searchable knowledge base, and allows users to ask questions through an intelligent AI chatbot.

---

# 🚀 Features

- 📋 Public Q&A Submission Form
- 🤖 AI-generated Tags using Google Gemini
- 🗄️ Automatic Data Storage in n8n Data Table
- 🔍 Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
- 💬 AI Chat Assistant
- 🧠 Conversation Memory
- ⚡ Built completely in n8n
- 🔄 No custom backend required

---

